variable [Fintype d₁] [Fintype d₂] [Fintype d₃] [Fintype d₄] [Fintype d₅] [Fintype d₆] [DecidableEq d₁] [DecidableEq d₂]

variable [DecidableEq d₃] [DecidableEq d₄] in
```

Now, we need to define the instance for `Nonempty (CPTPMap d₁ d₂)`. To do this, we can provide a witness. Let's define the zero map as our witness.

